<item>
            <title>[LU-127] lustre modules on rhel should require their kernel</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-127</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Since weak-modules is pretty much a non-starter on RHEL, we should restore the &lt;tt&gt;Requires: kernel = $version&lt;/tt&gt; dependency relationship between the lustre modules and the kernel they were built for.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="10447">LU-127</key>
            <summary>lustre modules on rhel should require their kernel</summary>
                <type id="1" iconUrl="https://jira.whamcloud.com/secure/viewavatar?size=xsmall&amp;avatarId=11303&amp;avatarType=issuetype">Bug</type>
